comment: I didn't get to do a single move when I played this, but it was short and funny I guess.

Took 5 years to play it! - - its a silly light game, but I do like the mechanism, and thats why Im keeping it (Rating 6.147, May 16). UPDATE: To be honest, the best strategy might be to not think at all and randomly select a token, and let everyone else worry - - so, sent to the Board Game Event Horizon (Dec 19). UPDATE: Pub Meeple Ranking Engine Dec 2020 (Rating: 3.188).
Not seen for a long time. Perhaps donated.
